query:
SELECT 
            DATE_TRUNC('hour', created_at) AS created_at,
            location.name as location,
            COUNT(*) as count
        FROM
            market_order,
            location
        WHERE
            location_id = location.id
            AND expires_at > NOW()
        GROUP BY
            DATE_TRUNC('hour', created_at),
            location.name
        ORDER BY
            created_at DESC
